00:00:07.260 --> 00:00:11.360
Second day at Gamescom and we are back on PES 2016 Preview

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:13.360
So we start with menus

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:16.280
Menus didn't change a lot actually

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:18.860
Drag and drop system if though more soft

00:00:18.860 --> 00:00:20.720
and they operate tiny visual ajustments

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:22.260
like player's photos and more statistics,

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:26.320
A card system according to players and goalkeepers

00:00:26.460 --> 00:00:31.240
And for strategy it's the same and you can manage your game plan

00:00:31.580 --> 00:00:33.480
by form, abilities, or manually

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:36.540
Graphics

00:00:37.170 --> 00:00:39.170
Graphics were improved in this gamescom code

00:00:39.170 --> 00:00:41.970
It's not a revolution but a cool evolution

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:43.420
faces are even better,

00:00:43.540 --> 00:00:46.280
the grass is green even in winter configuration

00:00:46.380 --> 00:00:49.600
lightning are quite good, the result is more convincing

